INSTALLATION of OpenLSS Core

1) Create config.php

example:

<?php

$config['info']['site_name'] = 'Foo Test';

$config['db']['host'] = 'localhost';
$config['db']['username'] = 'bar';
$config['db']['database'] = 'foo';
$config['db']['password'] = 'barbar';

2) Import database config

example:
mysql -u foo -pbar foo < lss.sql

or use phpmyadmin or whatever suits best

3) visit index.php in your web browser
4) see http://docs.openlss.com for documentation
4) start building your new software package
